19:20.125 --> 19:22.583
You guys are here
for a great cause.

19:22.583 --> 19:24.333
[cheering]

19:26.000 --> 19:28.458
But let's be honest,
you didn't pay to hear me talk

19:28.458 --> 19:30.750
